cs.DC, cs.NI, cs.SY, cs.DS, cs.GT 

Reasoning: 
- cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing) is the most likely category as the paper discusses a distributed load balancing algorithm for coordinating cloud service providers. 
- cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture) is also likely as the paper deals with coordinating resources across different cloud providers. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is a possible category as the paper discusses a coordination layer for the CloudShare algorithm. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of the Shapley value from game theory in the load balancing algorithm. 
- cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) is a possible category as the paper discusses the use of the Shapley value from game theory in the load balancing algorithm.
